  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Assistance for the Displaced Following the Recent Floods in the Provinces of Bujumbura Mairie, Bujumbura, Rumonge and Makamba</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to improve the living conditions of populations displaced by the recent floods in the provinces of Bujumbura, Bujumbura Mairie, Rumonge and Makamba (Burundi) through the provision of shelters and non-food items, support in site management / coordination, while ensuring protecting people and advocating for rights of access to land and decent housing.</narrative>
  </description>
